definition.value: Catalysis of the reaction -  sphingosine + UDP-D-galactose -eq- H(+) + psychosine + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  glucomannan(n) + GDP-mannose -eq- glucomannan(n+1) + GDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  GDP-D-glucose + glucose-6-phosphate -eq- alpha,alpha-trehalose 6-phosphate + GDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  estradiol-17alpha 3-D-glucuronoside + UDP-N-acetyl-alpha-D-glucosamine -eq- 17alpha-(N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl)-estradiol 3-D-glucuronoside + H(+) + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-D-galacturonate + 1,4-alpha-D-galacturonosyl(n) -eq- 1,4-alpha-D-galacturonosyl(n+1) + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ceramide + UDP-galactose -eq- D-galactosylceramide + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  heteroglycan + GDP-mannose -eq- alpha-D-mannosylheteroglycan + GDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  poly(glycerol phosphate) + UDP-D-glucose -eq- alpha-D-glucosylpoly(glycerol phosphate) + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  poly(ribitol phosphate) + UDP-D-glucose -eq- beta-D-glucosylpoly(ribitol phosphate) + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  GDP-mannose + undecaprenyl phosphate -eq- GDP + D-mannosyl-1-phosphoundecaprenol.
Catalysis of the reaction -  raffinose + 1-alpha-D-galactosyl-myo-inositol -eq- stachyose + myo-inositol.
Catalysis of the reaction -  poly(ribitol phosphate) + UDP-N-acetyl-D-glucosamine -eq- N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl-poly(ribitol phosphate) + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  lipopolysaccharide + UDP-D-glucose -eq- D-glucosyl-lipopolysaccharide + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  glycosaminoglycan + UDP-galactose -eq- D-galactosylglycosaminoglycan + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  polyprenyl phosphate + UDP-D-glucose -eq- polyprenylphosphate-glucose + UDP.

Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-N-acetyl-D-galactosamine + alpha-D-galactosyl-(1--gt-4)-beta-D-galactosyl-(1--gt-4)-beta-D-glucosylceramide -eq- UDP + beta-N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-(1--gt-3)-alpha-D-galactosyl-(1--gt-4)-beta-D-galactosyl-(1--gt-4)-beta-D-glucosylceramide.
Catalysis of the reaction -  sucrose + 1-alpha-D-galactosyl-myo-inositol -eq- raffinose + myo-inositol.

Catalysis of the reaction -  N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl-(1,3)-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-D-glucosylceramide + UDP-galactose -eq- D-galactosyl-N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl-(1,3)-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-D-glucosylceramide + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  beta-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-beta-N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl-R + UDP-galactose -eq- alpha-D-galactosyl-(1,3)-beta-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-beta-N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl-R + UDP.

Catalysis of the reaction -  N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-(1,3)-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-D-glucosylceramide + UDP-N-acetylgalactosamine -eq- N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-(1,3)-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-D-glucosylceramide + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2 bilirubin-glucuronoside -eq- bilirubin + bilirubin-bisglucuronoside.
Catalysis of the reaction -  sn-glycerol 3-phosphate + UDP-D-galactose -eq- 1-O-alpha-D-galactosyl-sn-glycerol 3-phosphate + H(+) + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  diphosphate + nicotinamide mononucleotide -eq- 5-phospho-alpha-D-ribose 1-diphosphate + H(+) + nicotinamide.
Catalysis of the reaction -  pyrophosphate + a 2,4-dioxotetrahydropyrimidine D-ribonucleotide -eq- PRPP + a 2,4-dioxotetrahydropyrimidine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  dTDP-L-dihydrostreptose + streptidine 6-phosphate -eq- O-(1--gt-4)-alpha-L-dihydrostreptosyl-streptidine 6-phosphate + dTDP + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  dolichol-phosphate + UDP-D-xylose -eq- dolichyl D-xylosyl phosphate + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  dolichyl D-xylosyl phosphate + protein -eq- dolichol-phosphate + D-xylosylprotein.
Catalysis of the reaction -  flavonol 3-O-glycoside + UDP-D-xylose -eq- flavonol 3-O-D-xylosylglycoside + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  peptide diphthamide + NAD+ -eq- peptide N-(ADP-D-ribosyl)diphthamide + niacinamide.
Catalysis of the reaction -  cytolipin-H + CMP-N-acetylneuraminate -eq- alpha-N-acetylneuraminyl-2,6-beta-galactosyl-1,4-beta-D-glucosylceramide + CMP.

Catalysis of the reaction -  D-galactosyl-N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-(N-acetylneuraminyl)-D-galactosyl-D-glucosylceramide + CMP-N-acetylneuraminate -eq- N-acetylneuraminyl-D-galactosyl-N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-(N-acetylneuraminyl)-D-galactosyl-D-glucosylceramide + CMP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  1,2-diacyl-3-beta-D-galactosyl-sn-glycerol + CMP-N-acetyl-beta-neuraminate -eq- 1,2-diacyl-3-[3-(alpha-D-N-acetylneuraminyl)-beta-D-galactosyl]-sn-glycerol + CMP + H(+).

Catalysis of the reaction -  alpha-N-acetylneuraminyl-(2--gt-3)-beta-D-galactosyl-(1--gt-3)-N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-R + CMP-N-acetyl-beta-neuraminate -eq- alpha-N-acetylneuraminyl-(2--gt-3)-beta-D-galactosyl-(1--gt-3)-[N-acetyl-alpha-neuraminyl-(2--gt-6)]-N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-R + CMP.

Catalysis of the reaction -  cytolipin-H + CMP-N-acetylneuraminate -eq- alpha-N-acetylneuraminyl-2,3-beta-D-galactosyl-1,4-beta-D-glucosylceramide + CMP. Alpha-N-acetylneuraminyl-2,3-beta-D-galactosyl-1,4-beta-D-glucosylceramide is also known as GM3.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (6AS,11AS)-3,6A,9-trihydroxypterocarpan + dimethylallyl-pyrophosphate -eq- glyceollin + diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  p-hydroxybenzoate + solanesyl pyrophosphate -eq- nonaprenyl-4-hydroxybenzoate + diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  sn-glycerol 1-phosphate + all-trans-geranylgeranyl diphosphate -eq- sn-3-O-(geranylgeranyl)glycerol 1-phosphate + diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  sn-3-O-(geranylgeranyl)glycerol 1-phosphate + all-trans-geranylgeranyl diphosphate -eq- 2,3-di-O-(geranylgeranyl)glycerol 1-phosphate + diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2 putrescine -eq- NH3 + sym-homospermidine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  a 2-oxo acid + L-asparagine -eq- an amino acid + 2-oxosuccinamate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (S)-3-amino-2-methylpropanoate + 2-oxoglutarate -eq- 2-methyl-3-oxopropanoate + L-glutamate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  keto-phenylpyruvate + L-tryptophan -eq- 3-(indol-3-yl)pyruvate + L-phenylalanine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  pyridoxamine + pyruvate -eq- L-alanine + pyridoxal.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (S)-3-methyl-2-oxopentanoate + L-valine -eq- 3-methyl-2-oxobutanoate + L-isoleucine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-oxoglutarate + UDP-2-acetamido-4-amino-2,4,6-trideoxy-D-glucose -eq- L-glutamate + UDP-2-acetamido-4-dehydro-2,6-dideoxy-beta-D-glucose.
Catalysis of the reaction -  glycine + oxaloacetate -eq- L-aspartate + glyoxylate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (2-aminoethyl)phosphonate + pyruvate -eq- L-alanine + phosphonoacetaldehyde.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (2R)-3-amino-2-methylpropanoate + pyruvate -eq- 2-methyl-3-oxopropanoate + L-alanine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  D-methionine + pyruvate -eq- 4-methylthio-2-oxobutanoate + L-alanine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-2,4-diaminobutyrate + pyruvate -eq- L-alanine + L-aspartate 4-semialdehyde.
